Healthcare Management System Using Agile
1. Introduction

A Healthcare Management System helps hospitals manage patient records, appointments, and medical reports digitally.

2. Objectives

To maintain patient records

To manage appointments

To improve healthcare services

3. Scope

The system includes doctor management, patient management, and report generation.

4. Agile Methodology

Development is done in sprints covering patient module, doctor module, and billing module.

5. Features

Patient registration

Appointment scheduling

Medical record management

Billing system

6. Advantages

Improved efficiency

Reduced paperwork

Better patient care

7. Conclusion

The Agile-based healthcare system provides flexibility, reliability, and improved service quality.
